00:10:44,766 --> 00:10:45,991
Scott: That's part of the MacBook.

170
00:10:46,653 --> 00:10:48,679
Scott: They have all kinds of Mac stuff in them.

171
00:10:49,761 --> 00:10:53,057
Scott: Windows has a lot of drivers, but does it have drivers for that stuff?

