00:56:42,551 --> 00:56:43,634
Scott: You know, this is going on.

879
00:56:43,654 --> 00:56:44,376
Scott: Do you want to do this?

880
00:56:44,798 --> 00:56:45,460
Scott: Oh, I saw something

881
00:56:45,480 --> 00:56:45,600
Scott: crazy.".

882
00:56:45,620 --> 00:56:46,301
Scott: Well, I

883
00:56:46,321 --> 00:57:05,400
Rym: guess the warning there is that, if you want to be the people like us, the ones who organize this for your group of friends, because someone has to do it, or you're going to have drama, be wary that your friends, while they're your friends, will become energy leeches, and will draw all of your energy, efforts, and attention for much of the con, managing them.

